==English==

===Plural noun phrase===
{{wikipedia}}
'''[[scramble]]d [[egg]]s'''
#A [[dish]] made by [[beat]]]ing and [[fry]]ing eggs, sometimes mixed with milk.

====Usage notes====
Although the plural form is most often used generically for the dish it is perfectly correct to use the singular when only one egg is used.

